Features:
- CStrike, DoD, EP2, Episodic, HL1, HL1MP, HL2, HL2MP, LostCoast, Portal on Source SDK Base 2013 Multiplayer
- Content mounter
- Mod directories containing the minimal amount of content needed to run the game

Requirements:
- Visual Studio 2013
- Multibyte MFC Library for Visual Studio 2013

Credits:
- Project by AlmightyToastz
- Content mounter by Joshuo Ashton from https://github.com/Joshua-Ashton/Source-PlusPlus